description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for a Full Remote Python Full Stack and AI Developer.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Write Python programs to integrate security testing tools in the DevSecOps pipeline, invoke automated scans
* Develop and integrate Rest APIs with access control to provide case status and reports
* Utilize Azure OpenAI frameworks to enhance AI Security testing
* Build dashboards using Python libraries (e.g., Pandas, Matplotlib, Plotly) to track case status from Kanban boards, delay per project/LOB/etc., Use Dataverse and PowerBi for data modelling and reporting as well;
* Deploy the solution in the Azure cloud
* Work closely with project managers, IT security staff, and system administrators to gather requirements, understand business needs, and develop solutions that improve security processes.
* Continuously evaluate and improve AI Security testing tool solution, leveraging new technologies and techniques, particularly AI and automation, to improve efficiency and effectiveness.









**Profile:** 



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* \\+5 years of hands\\-on experience with Python, particularly in frameworks like FastAPI, Flask, and experience using Azure OpenAI frameworks;
* Strong development skills required in the following areas,



 AI/ML and Python Full stack, fast APIs Development experience




 Agentic AI frameworks such as Microsoft AutoGen, Langchain




 Azure cloud resources such as Azure Open AI, Azure foundry, Azure web app, function app, Azure storage accounts.




 Model Context Protocol (MCP) and RAG concepts




 Technical Architecture Design and Critical Thinking



* Strong understanding of access control models such as Role\\-Based Access Control (RBAC);
* Experience in Dataverse, Power BI and reporting libraries in Python (Pandas, Matplotlib, Plotly, Dash) to build dashboards and reports;
* Ability to collaborate with various stakeholders, explain complex technical solutions, and deliver high\\-quality solutions on time;
* Experience working in Agile environments and familiarity with Scrum and Kanban methodologies for delivering the solutions;
* Fluent in English;

